725855f-b.title: Queens: 135th Avenue - 132nd Street
725855f-b.text:
One Hundred Thirty-fifth Ave., north side, west from 132nd
Street, showing in a set of three views the outbuildings on dacob
Bergen's farm.
1922.
Views 1,2 and 3.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAE BE REPRODUCED.
